
Bloodfist Help:  Socket

Guild level:  4
Honor Req:    0
Base Cost:    0

  You must have a chosen weapon at at least level 8 before you can do
this.  If you forge a chosen weapon with a socket in it, then you
can socket a gem inside the weapon giving it additional magical
properties.  Gems are one time use and can be saved in your private
room.

Usage:  socket gem

